oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Contest appearances by Mark O'Connor and others at the National Old Time Fiddle Championship held in Weiser Idaho. Also includes unknown fiddle tunes in a non-contest environment by an unidentified fiddler who may be Benny Thomasson.
